{"tid":2316558,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–熊貓渡過寒冬的一道妙計","createTime":"2020-12-08T03:23:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T01:46:16.000Z","uid":38861,"like":54,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"9a886c0a25ac97a3e7f0184a6105e12e4f7a0709","tid":2316558,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T03:23:14.000Z","msg":"上集我們講述了小臭鼩應對寒冬的一道機制，今集我們將會講述熊貓應付寒冬的一道怪招。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RmJgvvq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRmJgvvq.jpg&h=61ab036c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖2）有研究發現（Ref1)，當攝氏低過15度的時候，熊貓會將馬糞塗滿全身，而且選糞中亦有一定的揀擇，牠們並不會採用暴露於大自然間超過10日的馬糞。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LJ0VL27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLJ0VL27.jpg&h=364b51f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為何會塗糞上身，而且為何又如此揀擇呢？<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）最後科學家發現，新鮮馬糞含有一定份量的化合物，BCP/BCPO (beta-caryophyllene/caryophyllene oxide) ，而這些化合物具有抑壓負責感測寒冷的TRPM8蛋白質功效。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ODEjtgy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FODEjtgy.jpg&h=51a3418a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利用老鼠作實驗體，在牠們身體塗上BCP/BCPO液體以模仿熊貓塗馬糞的舉動，對比塗上鹽水的對照群組，塗上化合物液體的老鼠較傾向行走寒冷的地方，而且亦較少互相擁抱取暖。<br />\n<br />\n因此科學家推斷，熊腦大有可能透過馬糞中的化合物抑制身體的TRPM8蛋白質，以自欺欺人的方式盡量減低身體感知寒冷的能力，使自己感覺良好渡過寒冬。<br />\n<br />\n但為何熊貓會懂得馬糞中含有對應的化合物，那就還是一個無法拆解的謎。<br />\n亦有可能的是，馬糞還有另外的功用尚未被揭曉出來。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"teal\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7HO%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=e809b860\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7HO%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=ac0df919\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpotatopigtongue%2F&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7HO%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=4e46b737\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/</a><br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.pnas.org/content/early/2020/12/01/2004640117\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pnas.org%2Fcontent%2Fearly%2F2020%2F12%2F01%2F2004640117&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7HO%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=f80cdc68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pnas.org/content/early/2020/12/01/2004640117</a>"},{"pid":"a996b0a951f9080b0c9b949dcf15122b115802a6","tid":2316558,"uid":38861,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T03:24:09.000Z","msg":"真實影片:<a href=\"https://www.sciencemag.org/sites/default/files/120720-pandas.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencemag.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F120720-pandas.mp4&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7HO%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=03878d8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sciencemag.org/sites/default/files/1